\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Freedom to make life choices:
\f0\b0 \'a0Freedom to make life choices is the national average of binary responses to the GWP question \'93Are you satisfied or dissatisfied with your freedom to choose what you do with your life?\'94 ... It is defined as the average of laughter and enjoyment for other waves where the happiness question was not asked\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Generosity:
