\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Perceptions of corruption:
\f0\b0 \'a0The measure is the national average of the survey responses to two questions in the GWP: \'93Is corruption widespread throughout the government or not\'94 and \'93Is corruption widespread within businesses or not?\'94\
